h3 Avatar Groups
p.-text
  | Use avatar groups to group multiple avatars or add descriptive text such as a users name.
  | Render an avatar group by wrapping an avatar in the class <code>chi-avatar-group</code>.
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--3.chi-grid
    each color in colors
      if (color !== 'secondary')
        .-mb--1.chi-col.-w--6.-w-sm--4.-w-md--6.-w-lg--4.-w-xl--3
          .chi-avatar-group
            div(class=`chi-avatar -${color}`) L
            = `Label ${color}`
  .example-tabs.-pl--2
    ul.chi-tabs#example-avatar-groups
      li.-disabled
        a(href=`#webcomponent-avatar-groups`) Web Component
      li.-active
        a(href=`#html-avatar-groups`) HTML Blueprint
  .chi-tabs-panel#webcomponent-avatar-groups
  .chi-tabs-panel.-active#html-avatar-groups
    :code(lang="html")
      <div class="chi-avatar-group">
        <div class="chi-avatar">L</div>Label text
      </div>

